---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Data Processing Addendum">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Data Processing Addendum (DPA)</h1>
 
    <p>Last Updated:   March 7, 2026</p>

    <h2>1. Roles</h2>
    <p>Customer is the Controller. InsightHunter is the Processor.</p>

    <h2>2. Processor Obligations</h2>
    <p>InsightHunter processes data only on documented instructions and implements appropriate security measures.</p>

    <h2>3. Sub‑Processors</h2>
    <p>InsightHunter may use sub‑processors. A current list is available upon request.</p>

    <h2>4. International Transfers</h2>
    <p>InsightHunter uses approved transfer mechanisms such as SCCs where required.</p>

    <h2>5. Deletion</h2>
    <p>Upon termination, Customer Data will be deleted or returned.</p>

    <h2>6. Audits</h2>
    <p>InsightHunter will provide audit reports or certifications upon request.</p>

    <h2>7. Contact</h2>
    <p>Email: support@insighthunter.app</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
